      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Learn the Long Sword",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nSharp, flowing strikes are the\r\nsoul of long sword combat. The\r\nfearlessness of a \u003CCOL RED\u003EZinogre\u003C/COL\u003E and\r\nthe elegance of a \u003CCOL RED\u003EMizutsune\u003C/COL\u003E\r\ncombined are just the thing\r\nyou\u0027ll need to master \u0027em!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Zinogre and a Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "D\u00E9couverte de l\u0027\u00E9p\u00E9e longue",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "Bon, je t\u0027explique !\r\nPour l\u0027\u00E9p\u00E9e longue, les mots\r\nd\u0027ordre sont fluidit\u00E9 et\r\npr\u00E9cision. Combine t\u00E9m\u00E9rit\u00E9 du\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003EZinogre\u003C/COL\u003E et \u00E9l\u00E9gance du\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003EMizutsune\u003C/COL\u003E, si tu veux affiner\r\nta technique !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Zinogre et un Mizutsune",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Scopri la spada lunga",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "OK, \u00E8 ora di imparare: colpi\r\ncontinui e diretti sono il\r\nsegreto per combattere con la\r\nspada lunga. Per affinare le\r\ntue mosse, ti serviranno il\r\ncoraggio dello \u003CCOL RED\u003EZinogre\u003C/COL\u003E e\r\nl\u0027eleganza del \u003CCOL RED\u003EMizutsune\u003C/COL\u003E.",
